<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center">拉开三国序幕的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">是曹阿瞒、刘卖鞋、孙美男和诸葛宝宝</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">朕要讲的三国</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">依据的是<strong>《三国志》</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">要从<strong>袁绍</strong>讲起</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在罗贯中笔下</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">袁绍是漂亮的草包</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一手好牌打得<strong>稀巴烂</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201113/2f074ad7ee8a469fb96382c9c4786f29.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">很少人知道</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">现实中</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">东汉末年这盘<strong>狼人杀</strong>里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">小袁是个狼人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>6</strong>得飞起</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>146年</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>士族顶级代盐人</strong>——袁家</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">包下了<strong>河南</strong>七星级饭店</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">邀亲戚同事喝满月酒</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">听袁绍小baby哇哇大哭</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201113/dc286fe24f504f1c9d281ea3bfaaf7e1.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201113/6b40948bd1814648ae46a80d6572b2ed.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">外人眼里很风光</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">可在家里，帅小袁被排挤</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">弟弟袁术骂他是<strong>家奴</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只因小袁拿了<strong>韩国偶像剧的烂剧本</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201113/0e4b74355bb34ab7a1913a0711458d56.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">顶着丫鬟儿子的身份就罢了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还没等小袁长大</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">妈妈就去世了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">小袁成了没根的草</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">丧气得很</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">直到他知道了偶像<strong>王莽</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">听了他的先进事迹</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">知道卑微的他逆袭建立新朝</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>点击回顾史上最强穿越者 王莽 的故事</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">王莽真的不是穿越者吗？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他卸载了<strong>网抑云</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">发誓要像王欧巴那样逆袭</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">成为天选之子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201113/892beac23ff44b62938380e771856d23.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">毒鸡汤依旧毒</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">袁绍越努力学习</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">受到的鄙视越多</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">幸好二伯（袁成）<strong>英年早逝</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">收了他当养子，继承香火</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">继承了二伯的人脉和资源</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">学霸小袁20岁就当上了<strong>县长</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201113/e9e1d8b1ce0a46b88e8e768311d43eb8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">官位屁股还没坐热</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">二伯母去世了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">小袁辞职<strong>服丧三年</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">接着又给二伯<strong>补服丧三年</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">男人20-26岁的浪浪年华</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">小袁全拿来<strong>隐居服丧</strong>了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201113/8e26a1b422fe4266a53ff6f01a46e65c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">后汉的人生就像一颗巧克力</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你永远不知道下一颗是什么味道</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">因祸得福</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">文人名士看袁绍这么<strong>孝顺</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">纷纷来面基</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>喝杯老酒，交个朋友，攀个关系</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就像后来的半个诸葛亮和半个刘备</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201113/71ff7da26c6d41e5901a62c5e4090ac9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">面基人太多，一度造成交通堵塞</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">袁绍只好设了个VIP——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>非海内知名，不得相见</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">其中会员就包括<strong>曹操</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201113/e203e4b142ea4d7093d1d8d717c12aad.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">此时的东汉末年</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">乱成一锅粥</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">民间<strong>黄巾起义</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">农民揭竿要打倒灵帝集团</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">朝廷灵帝病倒</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>外戚和宦官互掐</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">官五代就有这个好处</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">朝廷的八卦和局势</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">袁绍从小听到大</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>汉和帝揭开了外戚和宦官当权的大幕</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>东汉这座大厦即将崩塌</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">要想独权，走王莽的路</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">必须同时铲除这两股势力</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">夺权的保命诀窍是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>不能自己动手</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">广交名士顺便隐居服丧的袁绍</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">老早就想好了夺权剧本</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">准备当<strong>幕后导演</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201113/f212fd3d1ac24f62878d88d8a7eaec3b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201113/d8d35154ceca4ec9b411dc8b6ac698da.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">顶着爸爸是国防部长、叔叔是丞相的光环</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">和服丧时攒下的声望</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">袁绍成功打入外戚头头<strong>何进</strong>的内部</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">何进是猪肉佬出身</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">全靠老妹牛掰当上皇后才逆袭</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">相比历代外戚头头</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">何进<strong>寒酸无谋</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">需要<strong>袁绍的声望和头脑</strong>加持</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201113/e0944d63ecb54842a3728f23e912ff55.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">袁家有行政权</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">袁绍现在急需何进的<strong>军权</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">何进提升<strong>袁绍</strong>为<strong>中央警备团团长</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">把他当作心腹后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">何进又把他升为<strong>军长</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">当时曹阿瞒也在军队里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">地位还比袁绍低</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201113/d3c3b5c474cf41279c78e6b3fe0826c4.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">何进哪里能想到</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>自己亲手送上的不是军权</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>而是即将插在他胸口的两把刀</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201113/a8a3e5221ed3409aa1eadc301ba641f8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>189年</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">灵帝拿到了<strong>病危通知书</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">纠结皇位传给谁</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201113/35899fab78f54f3783d340714bb6c7fd.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人最怕比较</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">谁蠢谁尴尬</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">败家了一辈子的灵帝</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">回光返照</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">决定把皇位传给庶子<strong>刘协</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201113/2812da8244cd4ca6b2747e443668549b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">按照<strong>长子继承制</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这不合规矩</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">灵帝也没时间为孩子铺路了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">把小儿子托给宦官头头<strong>蹇（jiǎn）硕</strong>后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就两脚一蹬了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">刘协是<strong>董太后</strong>养大的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">董太后和何皇后婆媳关系恶劣</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">刘协一旦上位</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">何家会从此没落</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">身为舅舅的何进毅然决然搅和这事儿</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">跟宦官<strong>刚到底</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201113/a1e07f5902e548c6957fde8194aaaf97.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">基于刘协上位</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">宦官能分掉何家权力</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">于是蹇硕<strong>先下手为强</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">打算暗中灭了何进</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>怎料，团队里有叛徒泄密</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201113/16c5982c086c49baa7acd170f8839cad.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">何进逃过一劫</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">蹇硕只好妥协，让<strong>刘辩</strong>上位</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但何进深知</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">蹇硕掌管着刘辩的吃喝拉撒</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">可以让刘辩不幸病故，也可以取得他信任</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">两者对他都不利</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">决定干掉蹇硕</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这时</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">掌控全局的袁大导演</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">开始导戏，挑拨离间</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">插何进<strong>第一刀</strong>——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201113/2c45fd0fb6994619bf8848f3c8b9190e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">猪肉佬拒绝上当</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他知道</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>想杀他的只有蹇硕一人</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>不是整个宦官集团</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但猪肉佬是个优柔寡断的人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">想法经常动摇</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">生怕只是自己一厢情愿</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">宦官们可能都想干掉他的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201113/a9e4c2574ba342c0a05e485f4a48e7cc.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这时</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">另一边</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">蹇硕找太监队友，组成<strong>十常侍</strong>（暗杀何进十人组）</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">其中有副队长<strong>张让</strong>和<strong>赵忠</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一级脑力工作者<strong>郭胜</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">没错</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他们就是<strong>灵帝亲口承认的“爸妈”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201113/0117da07847f4ed69eb107045a35f6ff.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">可张爸和赵妈拎得清</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">当年一介贫民的何皇后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">靠郭胜的关系进了皇宫</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">何进也从此放下屠猪刀，升官发财</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">再后来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">爱妃<strong>王美人</strong>生下刘协后，被何皇后干掉了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">灵帝很生气，要替爱妃报仇</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">眼看刘辩要成为<strong>没娘的草</strong>了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">张让等人<strong>拼了老命</strong>才救下了何皇后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这批太监替何家打江山</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">刘辩身上又流着何家的血</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">最好的养老计划是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>外戚宦官一起保卫着何家太子的皇位</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不用见血</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也能保证后半辈子吃喝不愁</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201113/78cb1e52e40646c09c8bb36173b62e3f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">太监们等同于何家的再生父母</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以十常侍都站在何进这一边</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">向何进<strong>告发了蹇硕</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">蹇硕再一次被背叛</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还没刺杀</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">自己就搭上了一条命</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">何进也终于不再动摇</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">知道宦官跟他是一头的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">决定先放宦官一马</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而此时</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">挑拨学大师袁绍<strong>又往何进心头插了一刀</strong>——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201113/61adfc4e8dee4668a759dd140abf5e96.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">21年前</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">同是外戚的窦武</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">几乎被宦官灭门</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">何进又又开始动摇了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他觉得宦官DNA里改不了吃屎</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">必须<strong>先下手为强</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">唉</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">要不说猪肉佬就是猪肉佬呢</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他并不知道</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>好好读历史，对一个人的成功有多重要</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>当年窦武为了独权，主动猎杀全部宦官</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>宦官们走投无路，才发起攻击</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而当年这场战役的前因后果</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">袁绍早就听长辈讲了无数遍</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201113/5afd98d93e004638adf534572813a69c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这个形势</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">何家人都看得一清二楚</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">目前小皇帝还小，妥妥的<strong>无权工具人</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">宦官也没兵权，<strong>不构成威胁</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">和宦官合作是双赢</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以何皇后坚决不同意何进团灭</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201113/d732d9c8b28548d7aac3a078f302c7dc.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">猪肉佬又又又开始动摇了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有道理，那就不杀吧</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">袁绍却继续吹耳旁风</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201113/98ea700c83f04bf1965229d560dbd6c7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">袁导演这波操作太骚</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">直接<strong>把何皇后归入宦官阵营</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">让何进以为妹妹想孤立他</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">好让何进直接开战</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">两股势力<strong>狗咬狗</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">袁绍坐收渔翁之利</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">于是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">外兵入京</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">洛阳大乱</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">何皇后只好妥协，<strong>炒了宦官集团鱿鱼</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">宦官集团也向何进求饶，希望<strong>回老家耕田</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这时袁绍不乐意了，建议何进<strong>斩草除根</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">何进还算清醒</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>不接袁绍这份订单</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">眼看着何进靠不住</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">袁绍露出狼人身份</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>假借何进名义</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>猎杀全城宦官</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">宦官走投无路，砍下了何进头颅</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">何进终究走了窦武后路</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201113/88fd0c9d57bf4c728ac456cf7d6d9883.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201113/16788f5b25e04b8e807a1de5278407ec.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">宦官以为结束了这一切</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">没想到好戏刚开始</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">幕后狼人袁绍<strong>加速猎杀宦官步伐</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">拿下了宦官的<strong>禁军权</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201113/3fbcdc5f6122449c99f68f214fd4b3bd.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他正式拉开了<strong>士族统治</strong>的帷幕</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他以为胜券在握</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">可以奔向偶像王莽的道路</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">怎料</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">城楼下的外兵——<strong>董卓军队抓了刘辩</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">正试图窃取袁绍的果实</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这只董黄雀</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">正是袁螳螂放进来的……</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>而袁螳螂的失策</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>换来了三国集团的开业大吉</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201113/692f8dcb55c844678e78a92697f9588d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
